# config/package-lists/desktop-firefox.list.chroot
# Firefox ESR with school-safe enterprise policy.
# Policy file shipped at: config/includes.chroot/etc/firefox-esr/policies/policies.json
#
# Hi+En localization. Telemetry/studies/Pocket disabled, camera/mic/location
# blocked, SafeBrowsing always on, ManagedBookmarks pin to learning portals.

firefox-esr
firefox-esr-l10n-hi
firefox-esr-l10n-en-gb
